153
00:06:13,230 --> 00:06:14,530
What was that?!

154
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:22,310
You know, with all this talk of eggs
and sausage, I'm getting hungry.

155
00:06:22,310 --> 00:06:23,970
We weren't talking about food.

156
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:32,240
It's so muggy.

157
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:34,990
We end up sweating as soon
as it gets a little crowded.

158
00:06:34,990 --> 00:06:37,260
It's getting to be
that time of the year.

159
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,990
It's hot!

160
00:06:38,990 --> 00:06:41,220
They haven't turned on
the air conditioning yet.

161
00:06:46,030 --> 00:06:47,400
Hold on!

162
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,740
It's hot!

